\c 49
\s UJakobe ubusisa amadodana akhe
\p
\v 1 UJakobe wasebiza amadodana akhe wathi\x + \xt Dute. 33.6-25.\x*: Buthanani ukuze ngilazise okuzalehlela ensukwini ezizayo\x + \xt Nani 24.14. Dute. 4.30. Isa. 2.2. Jer. 23.20. Dan. 2.28.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Buthanani, lizwe madodana kaJakobe, limlalele uIsrayeli uyihlo.
\p
\v 3 Rubeni, ulizibulo lami\x + \xt 29.32.\x*, amandla ami, lokuqala kokuqina kwami\x + \xt Dute. 21.17. Hlab. 78.51; 105.36.\x*, ukuphelela kwesithunzi\x + \xt 4.7 .\x*, lokuphelela kwamandla.
\v 4 Uphuphuma njengamanzi, kawuyikuba ngopheleleyo, ngoba ukhwele embhedeni kayihlo\x + \xt 35.22. 1 Lan. 5.1.\x*, wasu\add w\add*ona; wakhwela embhedeni wami.
\p
\v 5 USimeyoni loLevi bayizelamani\x + \xt 29.33,34.\x*; inkemba zabo ziyizikhali zokuphanga.
\v 6 Umphefumulo wami ungangeni emphakathini wabo wangasese\x + \xt Zaga 11.13; 20.19.\x*, udumo lwami lungahlangani emhlanganweni wabo\x + \xt Hlab. 16.9; 57.8.\x*; ngoba ngolaka lwabo babulala umuntu, langokuzithokozisa baquma izinkabi umsipha.
\v 7 Kaluqalekiswe ulaka lwabo ngoba lulamandla, lentukuthelo yabo ngoba ilesihluku. Ngizabehlukanisa koJakobe\x + \xt Nani 3.6. Josh. 19.1. 1 Lan. 4.27.\x*, ngibahlakaze koIsrayeli.
\p
\v 8 Juda, wena, abafowenu bazakudumisa\x + \xt 29.35; 27.29.\x*; isandla sakho sizakuba sentanyeni yezitha zakho\x + \xt 2 Sam. 22.41.\x*; amadodana kayihlo azakukhothamela\x + \xt 1 Lan. 5.2.\x*.
\v 9 UJuda ungumdlwane wesilwane\x + \xt Dute. 33.22.\x*; wenyukile empangweni, ndodana yami, uguqile, ulele njengesilwane, lanjengesilwane esisikazi; ngubani ozamsukumisa\x + \xt Nani 23.24; 24.9. Isam. 5.5.\x*?
\v 10 Intonga yobukhosi kayiyikusuka kuJuda\x + \xt Nani 24.17. Zek. 10.11.\x*, lomnikumthetho phakathi kwenyawo zakhe\x + \xt Hlab. 60.7; 108.8. Dute. 28.57.\x*, aze afike uShilo\f + \fk uShilo: \fl Heb. \fq lowo engeyakhe\f*, njalo izizwe zizamlalela\x + \xt Zaga 30.17.\x*.
\v 11 Ubophela ithole lakhe likababhemi evinini\x + \xt 2 Kho. 18.32. Isa. 5.2. Jer. 2.21. Hlu. 16.4. Nani 13.23.\x*, lethole likababhemikazi wakhe evinini elihle. Uwatsha isigqoko sakhe ewayinini, lesembatho sakhe egazini lezithelo zevini.
\v 12 Amehlo \add akhe\add* azakuba nsundu ngewayini\x + \xt Zaga 23.29.\x*, lamazinyo \add akhe\add* mhlophe ngochago.
\p
\v 13 UZebuluni uzahlala\x + \xt Dute. 33.18,19. Josh. 19.10,11.\x* ethekwini lolwandle\x + \xt Dute. 1.7. Josh. 9.1. Hlu. 5.17.\x*, abe litheku lemikhumbi, lomngcele wakhe uzakuba ngaseSidoni.
\p
\v 14 UIsakari ungubabhemi olamathambo alamandla, oqutha phakathi kwemithwalo emibili\x + \xt Hlu. 5.16. Hlab. 68.13. Hlu. 5.15. 1 Lan. 12.32.\x*.
\v 15 Wathi ebona indawo yokuphumula ukuthi inhle, lelizwe ukuthi liyabukeka, wagobisa amahlombe\x + \xt 1 Sam. 10.9.\x* akhe ukuze athwale, waba yinceku esibhalweni\x + \xt Eks. 1.11. Josh. 16.10.\x*.
\p
\v 16 UDani uzakwahlulela abantu bakhe\x + \xt Gen. 30.6.\x*, njengesinye sezizwe zakoIsrayeli.
\v 17 UDani uzakuba yinyoka endleleni, inhlangwana emkhondweni, eluma izithende zebhiza, ukuze umgadi walo awe nyovane.
\v 18 Ngilindele usindiso\x + \xt Hlab. 25.5. Isa. 25.9.\x* lwakho, N\sc KOSI\sc*.
\p
\v 19 UGadi, iviyo lizamhlasela\x + \xt Gen. 30.11.\x*, kodwa yena uzahlasela ezithendeni.
\p
\v 20 Kuvela kuAsheri, ukudla kwakhe kuzanona, uzaveza izibiliboco zenkosi.
\p
\v 21 UNafithali uyimpala ethukululiweyo, eveza amazwi amahle.
\p
\v 22 UJosefa ulugatsha oluthelayo, ugatsha oluthelayo emthonjeni, ingatsha\f + \fk ingatsha: \fl Heb. \fq amadodakazi.\f* zikhwela phezu komduli.
\v 23 Abatshoki\x + \xt 37.19 .\x* basebemphatha kabuhlungu\x + \xt 37.24,28; 39.20.\x*, ba\add m\add*tshoka\x + \xt Hlab. 18.14.\x*, bamzonda\x + \xt 27.41; 50.15.\x*.
\v 24 Kodwa idandili lakhe\x + \xt Jobe 29.20.\x* lahlala liqinile, lengalo zezandla zakhe zaqiniswa ngezandla zikaSomandla kaJakobe\x + \xt Hlab. 132.2,5. Isa. 1.24.\x*, okuvela khona umelusi, ilitshe likaIsrayeli\x + \xt Hlab. 80.1. Isa. 28.16. 1 Pet. 2.4.\x*,
\v 25 ngoNkulunkulu kayihlo\x + \xt 35.3; 50.17; 17.1.\x* ozakusiza, langoSomandla ozakubusisa ngezibusiso zamazulu ezivela phezulu, izibusiso zokujula okulele phansi, izibusiso zamabele lesizalo,
\v 26 izibusiso zikayihlo ziyedlula izibusiso zabokhokho bami, kuze kube sengqongeni zamaqaqa aphakade\x + \xt Dute. 33.15. Hab. 3.6.\x*; zizakuba phezu kwekhanda likaJosefa\x + \xt Dute. 33.16.\x*, laphezu kwenkanda yalowo owehlukaniswe kubafowabo.
\p
\v 27 UBenjamini uyimpisi edabulayo\x + \xt Hez. 22.27.\x*; ekuseni izakudla ekujimbileyo, lakusihlwa izakwehlukanisa impango\x + \xt Zek. 14.1. Hez. 39.10.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Bonke labo bayizizwe ezilitshumi lambili zakoIsrayeli; futhi lokho yikho uyise akukhuluma kubo ebabusisa; ngulowo lalowo ngesibusiso sakhe wababusisa.
\v 29 Wasebalaya wathi kubo: Sengibuthelwa ebantwini bakithi\x + \xt 49.33; 25.8.\x*; lingingcwabe labobaba\x + \xt 47.30.\x* obhalwini olusensimini kaEfroni umHethi\x + \xt 23.9; 50.13.\x*,
\v 30 obhalwini olusensimini yeMakaphela eqondane leMamre, elizweni leKhanani, uAbrahama owaluthenga lensimu kuEfroni umHethi\x + \xt 23.16,17.\x* ibe yindawo yethu yokungcwabela.
\v 31 Lapho bangcwaba oAbrahama loSara umkakhe\x + \xt 23.19; 25.9.\x*; lapho bangcwaba oIsaka\x + \xt 35.29.\x* loRebeka umkakhe; lalapho ngangcwaba uLeya,
\v 32 insimu, lobhalu olukiyo, kwathengwa emadodaneni kaHethi.
\v 33 Kwathi uJakobe eseqedile ukulaya amadodana akhe, waqoqela inyawo zakhe embhedeni, waphela, wabuthelwa ebantwini bakibo\x + \xt 49.29.\x*.
